# Quick setup

```
git clone zephyrnet.hackclub.com:/opt/zephyrnet/{{site}}/.git
cd {{site}}/
```

##...or push an existing repo from the command line

```
git remote add origin zephyrnet.hackclub.com:/opt/zephyrnet/{{site}}/.git
git branch -M main
git push -u origin main
```

# Deployment

If you have an index.html file, everything in {{site}} will be hosted at http://{{site}}.

